      "amount": "to taste"
    },
    {
      "name": "scallions (green onions)",
      "amount": "for garnish",
      "notes": "chopped finely"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat sesame oil in a wok over medium-high heat.",
    "Add garlic and sliced onions; stir-fry until fragrant and slightly golden, about 2 minutes.",
    "Pour in mirin, rice vinegar, salt, and pepper. Stir well to combine.",
    "Gently add pasta (or use rice if preferred) and toss together until heated through.",
    "Remove from heat and garnish with chopped scallions.",
    "Serve hot as a meal or side dish."
